description: Situated in vibrant South Boston, this exquisite 2 bedroom/2 bathroom condo epitomizes contemporary urban living. Built in 2019, this top-floor residence seamlessly blends modern aesthetics with functional design. The spacious living room has floor to ceiling windows, creating ample natural light throughout the entire unit. The kitchen features beautiful cabinetry, Italian Bertazzoni gas range, quartz countertops and a large 4-seater island. Both bedrooms are well-appointed with ample closet space and large windows. The primary bedroom features an en-suite bath with glass enclosed tile shower. Garage parking is included.The shared roof deck provides panoramic views of the city skyline and a perfect setting for outdoor gatherings. Other amenities include central air, in-unit laundry and a building elevator. With its prime location, residents enjoy easy access to the Seaport, Broadway T Station and South Boston's award-winning dining options.
